Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory260.png'}
{3: 'Dominik Memorial Park, Gestalt virtual space.'}
{3: 'Moving the video screen of the Eden 16-B region before his eyes, Murray watches the battle with a bemused expression on his face.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Murray', 3: 'The "Veritas" model...? I didn\'t know the Purifying Force was sent here.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Murray', 3: "But the way she fights... That's probably just a data mask. Whoever that is, that's not the real Bianca.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Murray', 3: 'I never thought my brother would be here as well.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Murray', 3: "Looks like I'll need a change of plans.", 4: '1'}
{3: "A sudden icy hint travels up Murray's spine."}
{3: '—And yet, the surveillance cameras and mirrors he set up beforehand show no one sneaking up on him.'}
{2: 'Murray', 3: 'To whom do I owe the pleasure?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Murray', 3: 'Hmm, not one for words? Then you must be an enemy.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Murray', 3: "In that case, I'll have to remind you something.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'The icy feeling has yet to reside, but Murray knows that whoever they are, they have taken the bait.'}
{2: 'Murray', 3: "—You've stepped on my welcome mat.", 4: '1'}
{3: "The iciness is immediately dispelled from Murray's neck. Three rows of iron spikes trail through the space behind him."}
{3: 'Murray quickly turns, pointing a primed data weapon at the emptiness before him.'}
{3: '—No one. But it cannot have been paranoia.'}
{2: 'Murray', 3: 'I see... Let me guess, the Scarab Squad?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Murray', 3: "Ahaha, let's have tea some other day. I'm afraid I'm still on a mission and will have to take my leave.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Murray hops off the platform, escaping through a zipline to the core area that was installed beforehand.'}
